3) Arts, Crafts & Sewing: Glitter colors are commonly used in arts and crafts projects, including nail art. This category includes various supplies for creative activities.

4) Office Products: Nail hardeners can also be used in professional settings, such as nail salons or beauty spas. This category includes products commonly used in office or business environments.

5) Home & Kitchen: Although less likely, this category could be relevant if the paper is discussing the storage or organization of nail products in the home or kitchen area.
